{"id": "1420332953850089524", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "897843515197898833", "author_name": "iibenigml1588", "content": "Covenants can be reused in dtide, so ppl often build a general set instead of one that’s strictly for a single awakener. Even for a dedicated set it also depends on the role of the char, support or dps.\nAs for aliemus, most of the time you don’t build it, unless the character can really make good use of it, like Tulu or GDoll", "timestamp": "2025-09-24T08:56:04.708000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["495650534905085962"], "reply_to": "1420284432824401984"}
{"id": "1420335794865963058", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "897843515197898833", "author_name": "iibenigml1588", "content": "You choose a carry and build around them, but I think it's a bit rough for your roster right now.  Corpo aurita team is decent but not easy to make it work early in. Salvador is good but needs e2/E3 to be a proper DPS, and you really want Thais. A good carry in standard is Jenkins, other slots you can choose from horla, winkle, orgier, Karen, naut, cassiah, Erica. If you like that team then you can pull for Clem and wait for castor rerun.", "timestamp": "2025-09-24T09:07:22.059000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["948019103518580866"], "reply_to": "1420257108934398036"}
